subject: Sailboats and Sailing
Volvo Ocean Race
lead_paragraph: A Dutch team led the seven-yacht-strong Volvo Ocean Race fleet out of Alicante, Spain, for the start of a nine-month marathon — straight into a Mediterranean storm on Saturday.
